author: ashish
msg: Code cleanup for error / success message in old implementation of AddItemRequest in eBay.
It is not good practice to break the process of exporting to eBay if some product don't have starting price.
Instead of this I have collected all the products in the list that don't have starting price and then returned this list at the end.
Also returned the list of products that has starting price and exported successfully to eBay.
Now after export the screen will looks like: http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2549/3924985627_60903d63bd_b.jpg
